docs.lead_paragraph: CHOLERA--THE HOSPITAL IN BROOKLYN.--As nearly as can be ascertained, five cases of Cholera were reported yesterday to the Board of Health. Four of these, it is stated, terminated fatally. There are many complaints made about the reports of Cholera cases, but they are as correct as can be obtained, under the circumstances.
